export default [
    {
        "category": "History",
        "type": "multiple",
        "difficulty": "medium",
        "question": "Which of these countries was NOT a part of the Soviet Union?",
        "correct_answer": "Afghanistan",

            "Turkmenistan",
            "Kazakhstan",
            "Uzbekistan"
        ]
    },
    {
        "category": "History",
        "type": "multiple",

        "question": "When did the Battle of the Bulge end?",

            "August 6, 1945",
            "December 7, 1941",
            "December 16, 1944"
        ]
    },
    {
        "category": "History",
        "type": "multiple",

            "42 BCE",
            "264 BCE",
            "102 CE"
        ]
    },
    {
        "category": "History",
        "type": "multiple",

            "1987",
            "1991",
            "1993"
        ]
    },
    {
        "category": "History",
        "type": "multiple",
        "difficulty": "medium",

        "correct_answer": "1869",

            "1850"
        ]
    }
